can we just pretend?

256
00:18:19.924 --> 00:18:21.841
Pretend to be like
we were before?

257
00:18:21.842 --> 00:18:25.720
No Osman. I'll leave
here. go to reception.

258
00:18:25.721 --> 00:18:27.138
